  <brief_title>Zimura in Subjects With Geographic Atrophy Secondary to Dry Age-Related Macular Degeneration</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2b Randomized, Double-Masked, Controlled Trial to Assess the Safety and Efficacy of Intravitreous Administration of Zimura™ (Anti-C5 Aptamer) in Subjects With Geographic Atrophy Secondary to Dry Age-Related Macular Degeneration</official_title>
  <sponsors>
